{"title": "New Organon Or True Directions Concerning The Interpretation of Nature", "description": "The Novum Organum is a philosophical work by Francis Bacon published in 1620. The title translates as \"new instrument\". This is a reference to Aristotle's work Organon, which was his treatise on logic and syllogism. In Novum Organum, Bacon details a new system of logic he believes to be superior to the old ways of syllogism. For Bacon, finding the essence of a thing was a simple process of reduction, and the use of inductive reasoning . . . This work was critical in the historical development of the scientific method. (Summary by Wikipedia)", "duration": 30642, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "1041", "name": "Francis Bacon"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCoverArt18/New_Organon_1205.jpg", "copyright_year": "1863", "genres": ["*Non-fiction", "Philosophy"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Alan Shaw"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "J. M. Smallheer"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Author's Preface", "readers": [3517], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/new_organon_0908_librivox/neworganon_00_bacon_64kb.mp3", "duration": 554}, {"section": 1, "title": "Book 1, Aphorisms 1-44", "readers": [3517], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/new_organon_0908_librivox/neworganon_01_bacon_64kb.mp3", "duration": 972}, {"section": 2, "title": "Book 1, Aphorisms 45-60", "readers": [3517], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/new_organon_0908_librivox/neworganon_02_bacon_64kb.mp3", "duration": 941}, {"section": 3, "title": "Book 1, Aphorisms 61-68", "readers": [3517], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/new_organon_0908_librivox/neworganon_03_bacon_64kb.mp3", "duration": 995}, {"section": 4, "title": "Book 1, Aphorisms 69-77", "readers": [3517], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/new_organon_0908_librivox/neworganon_04_bacon_64kb.mp3", "